<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p><b>When you install Hyrax for the first time it is pre-configured to serve test data sets that come with each of the installed data handlers. This will allow you to test the server and make sure it is functioning correctly. After that you can customize it for your data.</b>
</p>
